              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="supporter-info-box">
            <div class="info-icon">üí¨</div>
            <div class="info-text">
              <strong>Discord Access:</strong> Available exclusively for Ko-fi supporters.

              <a
                href="https://ko-fi.com/harryhopkinson"
                class="support-link"
                target="_blank">Support now ‚Üí</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="info" class="content">
      <div class="intro-section">
        <h2>üéØ What is R6 No Recoil?</h2>
        <p>
          A lightweight, efficient no-recoil tool for Rainbow Six Siege.
          Designed for smooth performance and ease of use, this open-source tool
          does one thing exceptionally well. &#8203 Without the bloat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="app-showcase">
        <div class="app-image">
          <img src="/app.png" alt="R6 No Recoil App Interface" />
        </div>
        <div class="app-details">
          <h3>üöÄ Built for Performance</h3>
          <p>
            Most recoil control tools are packed with features you'll never use,
            slowing down your system. R6 No Recoil is different ‚Äî it's optimised
            for low CPU usage and lightning-fast response times.
          </p>
          <p>
            With powerful config support and a clean interface, you get precise
            control without the complexity. Just download, run, and play.
          </p>
          <p>
            No installation required. Works seamlessly on Windows 10 and 11.
            Fully open source and customisable to fit your playstyle.
          </p>
          <p>
            Full controller support for Xbox and PlayStation (requires
            DS4Windows for PlayStation controllers).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>‚ö° Lightning Fast</h3>
          <p>
            Optimised for minimal CPU usage and instant response with no lag.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>üé® Powerful Configs</h3>
          <p>
            Extensive configuration options for every operator and weapon.
            Fine-tune your recoil control to perfection on top of custom
            keybinds and theme customisation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>üñ±Ô∏è/üéÆ Mouse and Controller Support</h3>
          <p>
            Works flawlessly with both mouse and controller setups. Full support
            for Xbox and PlayStation controllers (via DS4Windows for PlayStation
            (make sure it is running)).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>üíª No Installation</h3>
          <p>
            Just download, extract the zip folder and run the .exe file. No
            bloated installers, no unnecessary dependencies ‚Äî it just works.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="usage-steps">
        <h3>üéÆ How to Use</h3>
        <div class="steps-container">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <p>
              Click on the <code>Download Button</code> at the top of the website
              and extract the zip folder
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <p>Double-click to run the program (no installation needed)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <p>
              Choose whether you're Attacking or Defending (defaults to
              Attacking Operators)
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <p>
              Select your operator and primary weapon by clicking on the icons
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">5</div>
            <p>
              Use the <strong>Toggle Recoil Button</strong> to enable/disable the
              recoil control
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">6</div>
            <p>
              Use <strong>CapsLock</strong> (default) to toggle on/off during gameplay.
              Enable by clicking on the Toggle Key button
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">7</div>
            <p>
              Modify toggle keys, themes, controller support and more in the
              Config.toml file
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">8</div>
            <p>
              Enjoy improved accuracy and reduced recoil in Rainbow Six Siege
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>This tool is for educational purposes only.</strong> Windows Defender
          may flag it as a false positive due to the nature of input simulation. You
          can verify the safety by checking the file on VirusTotal.
        </p>
        <p>
          Always download from the official GitHub repository to ensure you have
          the real version.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <script>
      const parallax: HTMLElement | null =
        document.querySelector(".parallax-bg");

      const handleScroll = () => {
        const scrollY = window.scrollY;

        if (parallax)
          parallax.style.transform = "translateY(" + scrollY * 0.5 + "px)";
      };

      window.addEventListener("scroll", handleScroll);
    </script>
  </body>
</BaseLayout>
